{"word":"γυμνός","slug":"γυμνός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γυμνός, ή, όν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> <i>naked, bare</i> <a href='B:480 14:52'>Mk 14:52</a>; <a href='B:510 19:16'>Ac 19:16</a>;</b> <el>γ. <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κόκκος\">κόκκος</a></el> <i>bare</i> <i>seed</i> <b><a href='B:530 15:37'>1 Cor 15:37</a>;</b> <el>ἐπὶ γυμνοῦ</el> <i>over bare skin/body</i> <b><a href='B:480 14:51'>Mk 14:51</a>.</b> In extended sense: <i>without any covering</i><b> <a href='B:540 5:3'>2 Cor 5:3</a>; <a href='B:730 3:17'>Rv 3:17</a>; <a href='B:730 16:15'>16:15</a>; <a href='B:730 17:16'>17:16</a>;</b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pred.\">pred.</a> = <i>lie bare</i> <b><a href='B:650 4:13'>Hb 4:13</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> <i>inadequately dressed</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <a href='B:470 25:36'>Mt 25:36</a>, <a href='B:470 25:38'>38</a>, <a href='B:470 25:43'>43f</a>,</b> perhaps refer to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> left destitute of standard wear through indebtedness. <i>Without an outer garment</i> for appearance in public <b><a href='B:500 21:7'>J 21:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ foll.\">foll.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>poorly dressed</i></b> for a gathering <b><a href='B:660 2:15'>Js 2:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γυμνιτεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:γυμνότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}